<br>
I'll start hehe:<br>
1. Back when I was saving up for my fbss I had a good 5k saved up from minor trading, then I found a guy who really wanted a cane of the tranquil and a crested helm, but he only had an Argent Defender. So I traded him my Cane (which I had bought for 600pp the week before&lt;--good deal) and went and bought a crested helm from some guy for 800, and traded him. This was back when Argents were like 5k or more, so I imediately was able to sell the argent for 5k and bout my fbss that night. I was so happy hehe. (not to mention i had enough to buy back another cane of the tranquil right away too)<br>
<br>
2. Was on late night in NFP when some guy was sellin an Arbitors Greatsword, not many buyers that night so I gave him a tell and asked what he wanted. He said he didnt know he just wanted to go to bed, so I offered him 1500pp (all I had at the time) and he agreed. After playing around with it for a while (I'm not a big 2handed user so the 100dmg shots were interesting heh), I traded it and a rygor bp for my Green Jade Broadsword. (this was when arbitors were selling for 5k, GJB still goes for 8k). a 2500pp GJB, that was exciting as well =)<br>
<br>
3. And the most recent lucky deal was I found a guy who would trade me his Lamentation(10 to 11k) for my Silken Whip of Ensnaring(6k if you can find a buyer at all). So now I'm a dual lam fool hehe.<br>
<br>
I spend too much time in Freeport I think. Lets hear your stories! <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uamaretto.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Amaretto</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0> at: 6/27/01 8:13:32 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uraaj.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Raaj</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.screamdesign.com/graphics/webgraphics/free/other/bullets/u104.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>is a Formidable Opponent</span><br>  Posts: 153<br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/27/01 8:39:39 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Deal Gloating</span><hr size=1> Sword of skyfire for<br>
